title: Wildstorm Armageddon (complete)
description:
By request: the Wildstorm Armageddon event (complete)

From Wikipedia:

Wildstorm: Armageddon was crossover event in the Wildstorm Universe, written by Christos Gage and drawn by various artists.

Armageddon led into a number of bi-weekly series, Wildstorm: Revelations and Number of the Beast, which resulted in the relaunch of a number of Wildstorm titles.
